{
  "stem": "1363.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, but that-- those were, again, memories which I already aware of, very much so.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember, I brought home a little puppy whom I found on the street.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, and my grandmother throw me out with, with the dog together, sort of.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We can't afford to have a dog in the, in the apartment.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my mother was not around anymore.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She passed on.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So that's all--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What do you call war then?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The war started with me in '39.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In 1939, I was, as you know, a young kid of 12 years-- yeah.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that was the last time I saw my father.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because he was born originally in Vienna, in Austria.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he was not a Hungarian state person.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So when the Germans were tightening, or the Hungarian Nazis, the [NON-ENGLISH], were tightening the grip on the Hungarian Jews, he was one of them who wasn't allowed to stay in Hungary because he wasn't a Hungarian citizen.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'39.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he tried to get a permit or a visa into several countries in Europe.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And Belgium was the only place where they let him in.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, he spoke six languages.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That meant that French was a fluent language for him as well.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he had no fear to survive in Brussels, in Belgium.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he, he played a beautiful jazz piano and-- not classical as much.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But he did play classical as well.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he went as a pianist into Belgium, to Brussels.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he lived there for-- from '39 till '42.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he always tried to, to send some money home to Budapest.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "My mother was working as a secretary, clerical secretary.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And my brother and I went to school.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
